# WashedUp App Conventions

## What This App Is
Social activity app for finding people to do things with in Los Angeles. Not a dating app. Small groups of 3–8 people. Activity-first.

## Stack
- React Native + Expo Router (file-based routing)
- Supabase (auth + database) via `lib/supabase.ts`
- TanStack Query for data fetching (`useQuery`, `useMutation`)
- `expo-image` for images (not React Native's `Image`)
- `react-native-maps` + `expo-location` for maps/geocoding
- `lucide-react-native` for icons
- `expo-haptics` for haptic feedback

