- Supabase client: `lib/supabase.ts`
- Section detail screen: `app/plans-section.tsx`
- Schema reference: `docs/SCHEMA.md`

## Conventions
- `SafeAreaView` with correct `edges` on every screen
- `ActivityIndicator` color always `#C4652A`
- Ghost protocol (gender/age filtering) lives in `lib/fetchPlans.ts` — do not duplicate or modify
- No emojis in UI text
- Card border radius: 16px; button border radius: 14px
- Plan cards use `primary_vibe` aliased as `category` in the UI
